column6:
What would you like
to do today?

Now、 let's keep up
the good work!

I'll be happy
to help you
today as well!

This watch is a
very important object.

Would you be interested
in this watch?
Waaaa!　W- Where are you touching!?

To be of help to
Chronos、 that is my role!

Please say whatever you want.
I will help you!
Keep up the good work today.

Chronos、if you have a moment
please take
care of this.

This brush has
great power.
Are you curious?

If we take
it seriously、
we can do it!

Hmm～
……Eh!　How long have
you been watching me!?

My name is Rena.
I look forward to working with you.

I will do my best to serve
not only Chronos、
but everyone with sincerity.

The fairy of time
is here to
assist Chronos.

What do you need?
I am happy to answer
any questions.

Hmm……What a beautiful book……
Wha!　Chronos!
How long have you been there!?

What do you want
to do today?

What the hell?、
What are you
trying to sayー?

I hope this sword
has some
great power……

An opponent!?
I'll take care of it!

I am Astrea!
Nice to meet you!

Watching Chronos
battle makes me
want to battle too!

I'll show you
that even time
fairies can fight.

The history of mankind is
through battles!
What a tale!

If only I
were a little bigger
……I'd fight too!

Let me
know what you're
going to do today、OK?

If Chronos
asks me for a favor、
I'll help～

Chronos、
What are you doing?　
Want to play?

Even Maya does it
when she has to～♪

I'm Maya。
One of the
youngest time fairies

It's no use～、
but Maya can help!

Even Maya does it
when she has to～!
